May Edochie, first wife of the Nollywood actor, Yul Edochie, has called out her husband and his new wife on social media over the news of his child with the Nigerian actress, Judy Austin. Recall that the actor on Wednesday via his Instagram page announced the existence of his son and his marriage to the mother of the child, declaring her publicly as his second wife. He wrote, “It’s time for the world to meet my son. His name is STAR DIKE MUNACHIMSO YUL-EDOCHIE. “Born by my second wife @JudyAustin and I love him so much, just as much as I love my other children.” His first wife while reacting to his post wrote, ““May God judge you both.”